text: Kalateh-ye Luyedani is a village in the Zeberkhan Rural District in Khorasan province, Iran. According to the 2006 census, the population of Kalateh-ye Luyedani was 58 people who were part of 14 different families. == References == Category:Villages in Iran Category:Pages with unreviewed translations Category:Khorasan
